description: This is a Java Spring Boot controller class 'ResultController' that provides REST API endpoints for listing finetuning results and downloading associated artifacts.

classes.name: ResultController
classes.description: A REST controller for handling result listing and artifact download endpoints in a finetuning result API.

methods.name: list
methods.description: Handles GET requests to list all finetune results.

methods.name: artifact
methods.description: Handles GET requests to download the artifact associated with a specific result ID.
